{"tid":2354401,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"眼帯の喰種，其實你個人真係好撚假 (2)","createTime":"2021-01-05T12:30:20.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-05T12:57:14.000Z","uid":96439,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"9d172a7b63f2f5cf79033c6f275dec18e40ddfbe","tid":2354401,"uid":96439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T12:30:20.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"x-large\"><strong><span class=\"orange\">你話我之前搞鳩木耳，咁你依家做緊乜？</span><br />\n</strong></span><br />\n我返Pt  今日俾壽司郎藍田店店長炒魷魚 (2)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2354018\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2354018</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n呢個po本身個po主明顯係一個精神有問題嘅人，你係原po笑佢都算啦，<span class=\"x-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">你幫人開2算係咩意思？</span></strong></span><strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"orange\">係咪佢有病又冇名氣就抵死啲，你要推到佢仆街？</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><strong>其實你根本就係鍾意睇人仆街嘅人，不過見木耳有啲勢力就懶係嘢咁幫佢，見個呢個樓主咁多人一齊笑就落井下石。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"violet\">你話木耳係手足，搞鳩佢就係唔啱，但係呢個樓主都係手足，6月9號有份出黎遊行架喎！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RaNtqvL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRaNtqvL.png&h=4e8a76e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><strong><span class=\"orange\">你有冇諗過樓主比你不斷推po刺激會有咩後果呀？</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kqerWDK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkqerWDK.jpg&h=4bc744b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">之前仲係度扮清高？眼帶賤種，你收皮啦！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後附上賤種狗見到半節手指就發情的經過，大家自己判斷下呢個係咩人。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6ZZCcZ8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6ZZCcZ8.png&h=5a801343&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f5efac0d1b2e071065e5b8d802f42e7